"{\"uid\": \"out.com-gay-athletes-imane-khelif-legal-harassment-complaint-details\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By continuing to use our site, you agree to ourPrivacy PolicyandTerms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 77, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif files legal complaint for harassment over gender controversy  The Algerian boxer and gold medalist at the Paris 2024 Olympics is moving forward with an official harassment complaint following the outcry over her gender.\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 79, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999991180929352, \"rank\": 8.736929581526783e-07, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif at the Paris 2024 Olympics after winning the gold medal.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Algerian boxerImane Khelifis officially filing an online harassment complaint after getting caught up in a \\\"gender controversy\\\" involving several news outlets andcelebrities claiming that Khelif is transgender, which she is not.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's lawyer, Nabil Boudi, toldReutersthat this formal complaint was filed on Friday, August 9, andSky Newsreports that the legal document has been submitted to the Paris Public Prosecutor's Office.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999954989107, \"rank\": 4.50123652789732e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9999935754573845, \"rank\": 6.424584017108889e-06, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complaint reportedly notes that Khelif was the victim of online harassment while competing at theParis 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A press release shared by Khelif's lawyer reads as follows (as translated to English):  \\\"After the sporting time, comes the legal time.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having just won a gold medal at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, boxer Imane Khelif has decided to lead a new fight: that of justice, dignity, and honor.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms. Khelif contacted the firm which filed a complaint yesterday for acts of cyber harassment aggravated by the anti-online hatred center of the Paris Public Prosecutor's Office.\\\"\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999954989107, \"rank\": 4.50123652789732e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9999935754573845, \"rank\": 6.424584017108889e-06, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statement continues, \\\"The criminal investigation will determine who initiated this misogynistic, racist, and sexist campaign, but will also have to focus on those who fueled this digital lynching.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The unfair harassment suffered by the boxing champion will remain the biggest stain of these Olympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"-  (@)On Saturday, August 10, Khelif also shared the following statement with the press:\\\"All that is being said about me on social media is immoral.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to change the minds of people around the world.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imane Khelif at the Paris 2024 Olympics posing with her gold medal.Aytac Unal/Anadolu via Getty ImagesKhelif won the gold medal in the women's welterweight (66kg) eventat the Paris 2024 Olympic Games on Friday, August 9 after experiencing an onslaught of harassment fromcelebritiesand news outlets inaccurately claiming that the Algerian boxer is transgender.The last Olympic match that secured Khelif the gold was against Yang Liu of China.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.or